            "title": "杜特爾特訪港 現身灣仔為黨友拉票 外交公署：私人度假行程",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"菲律賓前總統杜特爾特訪港。AP\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/69c8343eb7f015f535d55558cb5b3c3e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031016172731223.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">菲律賓前總統杜特爾特訪港。AP</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>菲律賓前總統杜特爾特（Rodrigo Duterte）和其女兒、菲律賓副總統薩拉（Sara Duterte）近日來港，昨日（9日）出席在修頓場館舉行、為黨友拉票的集會。外交部駐港公署發言人回應有關提問時表示，杜特爾特和薩拉此次來港是私人度假行程，而有關菲律賓公民在港舉行的集會，已根據特區法律法規事先提出申請。\n\n</p><h2><strong>外交公署：菲公民在港集會按特區法規事前申請</strong></h2>\n<p>杜特爾特任內鐵腕掃毒，被國際刑事法庭（ICC）指控他違反「反人類罪」，據報擬對其發出逮捕令。杜特爾特在昨日集會上致辭時表示，自己竭盡所能，希望菲律賓民眾生活安穩，如果被判入獄則「無能為力」。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/society/3436018/%E8%8F%B2%E5%BE%8B%E8%B3%93%E5%89%8D%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E6%9D%9C%E7%89%B9%E7%88%BE%E7%89%B9%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF-%E4%BF%AE%E9%A0%93%E5%A0%B4%E9%A4%A8%E7%82%BA%E9%BB%A8%E5%8F%8B%E6%8B%89%E7%A5%A8-%E5%A4%A7%E6%89%B9%E5%9C%A8%E6%B8%AF%E8%8F%B2%E5%BE%8B%E8%B3%93%E4%BA%BA%E5%88%B0%E5%A0%B4\">菲律賓前總統杜特爾特秘密來港 修頓場館為黨友拉票 大批在港菲律賓人到場</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128182/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"杜特爾特秘密來港。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c068ff7fd41146cbbe97a353f3f302a4/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-09_at_6_49_23_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        杜特爾特秘密來港。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128180/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"二千多名在港菲律賓工作人士入埸參與大會。AFP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3a732de3fe145c9b38b0a96feb735da4/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-09_at_6_49_55_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        二千多名在港菲律賓工作人士入埸參與大會。AFP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128167/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"有支持者手持杜特爾特的畫像到場。陳亦龍攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c07e6a84768209877f5663d8044b1b4f/2025-03/KF_-_2025-03-09T190236_195.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        有支持者手持杜特爾特的畫像到場。陳亦龍攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4128168/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"杜特爾特來港出席集會，場館附近「萬人空巷」。陳亦龍攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f21e428752de93e8c98a4d8862a16189/2025-03/KF_-_2025-03-09T190215_476.png\" typeof=\"foaf:I