            "title": "戶戶送撤出｜網民聞消息愕然 外賣員留言感激：多謝袋鼠過去幾年養活自己",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f4f1b65d35b39476d7c0ffa289f21cbd/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031016131724286.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>攻港9年的戶戶送Deliveroo今日（10日）宣布，決定撤出香港市場，平台運行至4月7日後停運，並將出售部分資產予Foodpanda以及結束其他業務。大批網民在社交平台熱烈討論，其中有人指戶戶送早前曾找谷德超等人拍攝多個廣告大力宣佈，未料到這麼快會撤出香港。另有外賣員對戶戶送撤港感到不捨，「多謝袋鼠過去幾年養活到自己」。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/breaking-news/3436243/%E6%88%B6%E6%88%B6%E9%80%81Deliveroo%E6%92%A4%E5%87%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%B0%87%E7%87%9F%E9%81%8B%E8%87%B34%E6%9C%887%E6%97%A5-%E9%83%A8%E4%BB%BD%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2%E5%94%AE%E4%BA%88Foodpanda\">戶戶送Deliveroo撤出香港 將營運至4月7日 部份資產售予Foodpanda</a></strong>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129433/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"有外賣員感激戶戶送。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ce17d7fa4d1fa68fcf1b22d3983d7f80/2025-03/C.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        有外賣員感激戶戶送。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129435/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"大批網民對於戶戶送撤出香港感到愕然。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/59c3a367f3895ba18121d560b5930432/2025-03/A.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大批網民對於戶戶送撤出香港感到愕然。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129434/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"大批網民對於戶戶送撤出香港感到愕然。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/baf7a0a10d6d72609e96165b8f37f488/2025-03/B.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大批網民對於戶戶送撤出香港感到愕然。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129432/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"大批網民對於戶戶送撤出香港感到愕然。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7c4c854b0b4c2d5829a71adb6610fffa/2025-03/d1.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大批網民對於戶戶送撤出香港感到愕然。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129431/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"大批網民對於戶戶送撤出香港感到愕然。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8f7f34134ef8644668ff9bd8be82d361/2025-03/E.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大批網民對於戶戶送撤出香港感到愕然。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129430/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"大批網民對於戶戶送撤出香港感到愕然。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/33c0e42ade4c25d61eacb80c5f0e586f/2025-03/F.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大批網民對於戶戶送撤出香港感到愕然。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>戶戶送Deliveroo撤出香港市場消息傳出後，多名網民議論紛紛，其中有人指戶戶送近年被Foodpanda及Keeta夾擊，懷疑敵不過時代的洗禮，「要來的始終要來」、「捱到而家係奇跡」、「只係識搵明星賣廣告，間唔中就搞某某餐廳半價，搞果時懟爆某間餐廳，搞完咪又拍烏蠅」、「又少咗個平台做單」、「情願做熊奴，不願做團奴」、「等睇獨攬大權」、「俾美團徹底擊退」。\n\n</p>\n<p>另外，有外賣員對戶戶送撤港感到不捨，並感謝袋鼠過去幾年養活到自己，帖文隨即引來其他外賣員留言，「我真係初代做到依家，其實我真係唔覺得係講到咁差，佢套方式其實同之前Uber eats 差不多，首先一定係自由，完全無限時間，二嚟如果真係咁差，睇下平時搞擺工嗰班人係對邊間公司多？熊貓認第二，邊個敢認第一」。不過，有人認為戶戶送於4月7日撤出香港，對步兵影響不大。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關報道：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/breaking-news/3436256\" target=\"_blank\">戶戶送撤出｜Foodpanda母公司：Deliveroo現時客戶及送遞員 將被導向至Foodpanda</a></strong>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129259/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"戶戶送Deliveroo平台外賣員收到相關通告。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/91e0921262c9007c8f7bea064e69b9fa/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1015_13_51_2e595238_1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        戶戶送Deliveroo平台外賣員收到相關通告。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129365/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Deliveroo香港將出售部分資產予Foodpanda。何健勇攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/111c89e6cf783b58868f37af6996eaea/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250310_153344118_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Deliveroo香港將出售部分資產予Foodpanda。何健勇攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129303/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"戶戶送Deliveroo在港營運9年。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/915722aa817ac16ac3f41ccae981d1da/2025-03/BS20240115DELIVEROO001.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        戶戶送Deliveroo在港營運9年。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129302/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"戶戶送Deliveroo在港營運9年。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e2fe8ba3044229137982f3a22cbf0dd6/2025-03/BS20240115DELIVEROO017.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        戶戶送Deliveroo在港營運9年。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129307/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"戶戶送香港平台將繼續運行至4月7日。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f130aa857965e284225f14f9aa7f86bb/2025-03/NL230810FD008.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        戶戶送香港平台將繼續運行至4月7日。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4129308/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"戶戶送香港平台將繼續運行至4月7日。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/42f0ed4e4d4262264125f26183252b94/2025-03/NW231229FOOD08.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        戶戶送香港平台將繼續運行至4月7日。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
